# CivicFlow MY Mobile — environment example
#
# The demo runs FULLY OFFLINE with deterministic fixtures and needs NO secrets.
# Everything below is OPTIONAL. Copy to `.env.local` only if you want to enable
# the optional LLM path. Never commit a real key. All demo data is synthetic.

# Optional: enable the Anthropic LLM path for richer drafting/classification.
# When unset, the deterministic engine is used (recommended for demos/judging).
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the model used when an API key is present.
# CIVICFLOW_LLM_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8

# Optional: force deterministic mode even if a key is present (1 = force).
# CIVICFLOW_FORCE_DETERMINISTIC=1
